Rules.InvariantScript:
With({primColor: If(cmp_MD_Button_4.displayMode=DisplayMode.Disabled, cmp_MD_Button_4.disabledColor, cmp_MD_Button_4.primaryColor)},
If(
    cmp_MD_Button_4.outlinedButton, cmp_MD_Button_4.backgroundColor,
    primColor)
)

/*Switch(
    cmp_MD_Button.align,
    Align.Left, LayoutJustifyContent.Left,
    Align.Right, LayoutJustifyContent.Right,
    LayoutJustifyContent.Center)*/
cmp_MD_Button_4.align

CustomProperties.Name: align
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Align text and image inside button

CustomProperties.Name: iconSize
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A customIcon Size in relation to button height property

CustomProperties.Name: outlinedButton
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Outlined Button instead of Contained Button

CustomProperties.Name: outsideMargin
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Margin of the Button to all sides

CustomProperties.Name: primaryColor
CustomProperties.Tooltip: primaryColor in Hex code, on Positive Button the Fill

CustomProperties.Name: backgroundColor
CustomProperties.Tooltip: backgroundColor, on Positive Button the Text

CustomProperties.Name: adjustPaddingLeft
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Position of Icon from left side of button
